  "text": "In the second line, we rewrote the wavefunction in variables suited to the asymptotic region consistent with the above reflection amplitude as in the graviton case. We can now see easily that the asymptotic behavior is Φ tach (ρ) ≡ T (ρ) = µe Liouville theory, and we can extend the understanding gained in that case [CITATION_1] to this one.",
